<Speech gate:gateId="84012" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="83416" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="84142" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="83655" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="83546" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δριβελέγκας</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Μα, κύριε Πρόεδρε, δεν δέχθηκε τη διακοπή. Δικαίωμά του ήταν.</Speech></Speech>
